::Annihilator::

"Are you crazy! We can destroy these fools with our technology!" Annihilator 
yells, ducking under the shots, hearing a slight explosion as they hit a 
console. He rolls behind a panel, still not firing at Unitron.

"Come on, we can be unstoppable. We could return to Cybertron and rule!"
